title Activity Diagram: Complete Bus Tracking System Workflow

|Passenger|
start
:<b>Open Web App (PWA)</b>;

|System (Backend)|
:<b>Check Session State</b>;
if (<b>User Logged In?</b>) then (No)
 :<b>Prompt Login</b>;
 :Validate Credentials
 (Firebase Auth);
 if (<b>Valid?</b>) then (No)
 :Show \"Auth Failed\";
 detach
 else (Yes)
 :Retrieve User Role;
 endif
else (Yes)
 :<b>Auto-Login</b>;
endif

' --- ROLE BASED BRANCHING ---
split
 ' ==============================
 ' PASSENGER WORKFLOW
 ' ==============================
 |Passenger|
 :Load <b>Passenger Dashboard</b>;
 :<b>Search for Route/Bus</b>;
 
 |System (Backend)|
 :Fetch <b>Route Data</b> (Static);
 :Subscribe to <b>Live Location</b>
 (Firebase Listener);
 
 |Passenger|
 repeat
 :<b>Receive Live Coordinates</b>;
 :<b>Calculate ETA</b>
 (Distance / Speed);
 :<b>Render Bus on Map</b>;
 :Wait for Next Update;
 repeat while (<b>Viewing Map?</b>) is (Yes)
 detach

split again
 ' ==============================
 ' DRIVER WORKFLOW
 ' ==============================
 |Driver|
 :Load <b>Driver Dashboard</b>;
 :Select <b>Assigned Bus & Route</b>;
 
 if (<b>GPS Permission?</b>) then (Denied)
 :Show \"GPS Required\";
 detach
 else (Granted)
 :<b>Tap \"START TRIP\"</b>;
 endif

 |System (Backend)|
 :Update Bus Status to <b>ACTIVE</b>;

 |Driver|
 repeat
 :<b>Capture Smartphone GPS</b>
 (Lat, Lng, Speed);
 
 if (<b>Signal Valid?</b>) then (Yes)
 if (<b>Online?</b>) then (Yes)
 |System (Backend)|
 :<b>Sanitize Data</b>;
 :<b>Sync to Database</b>;
 else (No)
 |Driver|
 :<b>Cache Data Locally</b>;
 endif
 else (No)
 :Discard Weak Signal;
 endif
 
 :Wait 5 Seconds;
 repeat while (<b>\"STOP TRIP\" Pressed?</b>) is (No)

 |System (Backend)|
 :Update Bus Status to <b>IDLE</b>;
 detach

split again
 ' ==============================
 ' ADMIN WORKFLOW
 ' ==============================
 |Admin|
 :Load <b>Admin Dashboard</b>;
 
 if (<b>Select Action</b>) then (Monitor Fleet)
 :View <b>Live Fleet Map</b>;
 note right
 Observes all active
 buses simultaneously
 end note
 else (Manage Data)
 :<b>Add/Edit Route or Bus</b>;
 |System (Backend)|
 :<b>Commit Changes to DB</b>;
 :Log Admin Activity;
 endif
 detach

end split

stop
